Frontend

Framework: Next.js 14+ (App Router)
Language: TypeScript
Styling: TailwindCSS + shadcn/ui
State Management: Zustand / React Context
Form Handling: React Hook Form + Zod
Icons: Lucide React
Animations: Framer Motion (optional)

Backend

Runtime: Node.js 20+
Framework: Next.js API Routes (atau Express.js)
Language: TypeScript
Validation: Zod
ORM: Prisma (recommended) atau Drizzle ORM

Database

Primary DB: PostgreSQL (production) / SQLite (development)
Caching: Redis (optional, untuk performance)
File Storage: Local / AWS S3 / Cloudflare R2

Authentication

Solution: NextAuth.js / Clerk / Supabase Auth
Providers: Email/Password, Google OAuth

Deployment

Platform: Vercel / Netlify / Railway
CI/CD: GitHub Actions
Monitoring: Sentry / LogRocket